metadata.name: escape from reality by dima polanski
metadata.description:
exclusive free mint to moneyneversleep card holders & pobedeen pass holders

Have you ever mistaken your memories with your own dreams? Has there ever happened that some point in your life wasn’t actually one of your experiences, but of a movie character?

I, as many others, escape into other realities, and photography has become the most realistic getaway from reality.

piece by Dima Polanski

https://twitter.com/dimapolanski
